name: Javonte Green
comments: Green did not see the floor in Saturday's Game 3 win over the Heat.

name: Vincent Poirier
comments: Poirier (personal) is not on the Celtics' injury report ahead of Tuesday's Game 1 against Miami.

name: Nicolas Claxton
comments: Claxton will miss the resumption of the 2019-20 season after undergoing arthroscopic labrum repair surgery on his left shoulder Wednesday, Anthony Puccio of NetsDaily.com reports.

name: Dwight Powell
comments: Powell (Achilles) has no movement limitations and would be able to scrimmage, Brad Townsend of The Dallas Morning News reports.

name: Seth Curry
comments: Curry ended with 22 points (9-11 FG, 4-4 3Pt), three assists and one steal in 31 minutes during Friday's 130-122 loss to the Clippers.

name: Torrey Craig
comments: Craig is probable for Friday's game against the Clippers due to right knee soreness.

name: Kevon Looney
comments: Looney (abdomen) went "full bore" during Thursday's practice without restrictions, Connor Letourneau of the San Francisco Chronicle reports.

name: Ky Bowman
comments: Bowman finished with 11 points (5-6 FG, 1-2 3Pt), four rebounds and one assist in 24 minutes during Tuesday's 131-107 loss to the Clippers.

name: Goran Dragic
comments: Dragic (foot) is considered doubtful to play in Friday's Game 5 against the Lakers, Malika Andrews of ESPN reports.

name: Dennis Smith Jr.
comments: Smith (coach's decision) didn't see the floor in Tuesday's 122-115 loss to the Wizards.

name: Mike Scott
comments: Scott notched 17 points (7-12 FG, 3-4 3Pt), four rebounds, one assist and one steal in 22 minutes during Tuesday's loss to the Suns.

name: Tyler Zeller
comments: Zeller (knee) will not play Sunday against the Pelicans, Paul Garcia of ProjectSpurs.com reports.

name: Dewan Hernandez
comments: Hernandez (ankle) is with the Raptors in Orlando and is available to play, Austin Kent of SLAM reports.
